{
 "name": "RPlog_Orson_s_Warning",
 "title": "Orson's Warning",
 "summary": "In the personal barracks at Karrde's base on Myrkr, the mechanic Orson confides in the Jedi Jessalyn Valios, troubled by a vision and the path ahead for their group. The two talk through his fitness training and his half-joking wish to learn some lightsaber moves, the lighter banter masking a weightier unease about what is coming. Orson lingers at the window, lost in thought, before quietly taking his leave. The scene captures the quiet foreboding shared between the pair as darker events loom.",
